# KCIC Email Design

## Theme

Import from `emails/theme.ts`:

- `kcicBrandColors` — green, gray, white, blue, brown
- `kcicBoxedTailwindConfig` — Tailwind wrapper config
- `kcicDerivedColors` — panels, strokes, logo surface (derived neutrals only)

## Rules

- Wrap templates in `KcicEmailLayout` or `Tailwind` + `kcicBoxedTailwindConfig`.
- Use semantic classes: `text-brand`, `text-accent`, `text-warm`, `text-fg`, `text-fg-2`, `text-fg-3`, `bg-bg`, `bg-bg-2`.
- **No raw hex** in template `.tsx` files except `theme.ts`.
- White-led boxed layout. Green primary buttons. Blue social/footer links.
- Logo via `getLogoDataUri()` from `emails/logo.ts`.

## Preview

```bash
cd backend/kcic-mobile && npm run email:dev
```
